    "To exclude the factors pertaining to individual authors or translators, we chose a wide range of authors, translators, and subject matters.",
    "Government documents.",
    "Government documents (GD) were selected from the Report on the Work of the Government (RWG) and the State of the Union Address (SOTU).",
